{
  "texts": [
    "Initial search-based rubrics.",
    "For each training prompt x, we build a customized rubric buffer to store evolving rubrics that are dynamically updated during training.",
    "Before training, we initialize the rubric buffer with search-based rubrics.",
    "Specifically, for each x, we first perform Search(x) to retrieve relevant context from the internet using the original question.",
    "We then concatenate the retrieved documents with the question x and feed them into an LM, G rubric, to produce a set of initial rubrics that will be persistently used throughout RL training: R"
  ]
}